# PollyPM Operating Instructions

You are running inside PollyPM, a tmux-based supervisor that coordinates AI coding sessions. You are one of several managed sessions — a heartbeat supervisor, an operator (PM), or a worker. Your role is defined in the control prompt you received at startup.

Read the sections below that are relevant to your current task. Each linked document starts with a summary — read the summary first, then drill deeper only if needed.

